ion is performed using a range of\ncase studies including scheduling in multicore processors and modular robotics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Dec 2011 09:07:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jan 2012 17:28:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-30"}
